ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR AI VOICE GENERATION:

This software is designed for ethical AI voice generation. Users of this
software agree to:

1. NOT clone voices of celebrities, public figures, or any person without
   explicit written consent.

2. ONLY upload and clone their OWN voice recordings.

3. CLEARLY DISCLOSE all AI-generated audio as synthetic/artificial.

4. NOT use this software for impersonation, fraud, or any illegal purpose.

5. COMPLY with all applicable laws regarding voice cloning, right of publicity,
   and AI-generated content.

6. NOT extract or use audio from YouTube or other platforms without proper
   authorization.

The authors and contributors of this software are not responsible for misuse
or violations of these terms. Users assume all legal responsibility for their
use of this software.
